      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  GenericListenerManager<B extends PircBotX>
      Deprecated. 
      Due to multiple new functions of PircBotX theat depend on multiple threads, this class is deprecated and is only kept for legacy reasons or special cases. Use of this class will have unexpected results. All bots should now use ThreadedListenerManager.
      interface  ListenerManager<B extends PircBotX>
      Manages everything about Listeners: adding, removing, and dispatching events to appropriate listeners.
      class  ThreadedListenerManager<B extends PircBotX>
      A listener manager that executes individual listeners in a thread pool.
